longBusinessSummary: Discovery Minerals Ltd. operates as an acquisition and development company that targets natural resource properties. It focuses on gold mining projects. Discovery Minerals Ltd. was formerly known as Dhanoa Minerals Ltd. and changed its name to Discovery Minerals Ltd. in August 2012. The company was incorporated in 2005 and is based in Los Angeles, California.
